
=======
Changes
=======


0.2.1 (*2019-08-06*)
====================

- Support drawing tasks in left-to-right layout using `--horizontal` or `-h` option


0.2.0 (*2019-07-27*)
====================

- Support drawing tasks in execution order using `--reverse` option


0.1.1 (*2018-07-10*)
====================

- improve description given by `doit help graph`
- print name of generated file


0.1.0 (*2018-07-07*)
====================

- initial release

